article.headline: High Point 93, Warren Wilson 23
article.story: HIGH POINT, N.C. (AP) -- Mike Jefferson scored 15 points, Arizona Reid added 14 points and 10 rebounds and High Point routed Warren Wilson 93-23 on Monday night. Ibrahim Appiah scored 13 points, Eugene Harris added 11 and Matt Boswell scored 10 for the Panthers (2-2), whose largest lead was 72. High Point held a 55-10 halftime lead. Aleks Spasovski had 10 points and was the only player in double figures for Warren Wilson (2-6), a member of the United States Collegiate Athletic Association.
